        "title": "fix(opencode-go): disable thinking for minimax-m3 anthropic-messages path",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nMinimax models on the Anthropic Messages path return thinking content as regular text blocks rather than proper type:thinking blocks. This injects thinking: { type: disabled } for minimax-m3, preventing internal reasoning from leaking to channel output.\n\n## Changes\n\n`extensions/opencode-go/stream.ts`: Add createOpencodeGoMinimaxNoThinkingWrapper that identifies minimax-m3 and injects disabled thinking into the request payload.\n\n## Evidence\n\n```\npnpm exec vitest run extensions/opencode-go/\n  Test Files  5 passed (5)\n       Tests  28 passed (28)\n```\n\n**Label**: bug\n_AI-assisted._",
